  "engines": [
    "Obrix"
  ],
  "description": "Maximum air=1.0 and distance=0.8 — the furthest spatial position available in OBRIX, combined with the maximum air presence. This preset lives at the edge of perception: you feel it more than hear it. Wavetable (Standard bank) + Sine, with proc1=LP tuned to 1600 Hz for crystalline clarity without harshness. The shimmer quality comes from unison detune 0.15 (subtle beating) and coprime LFOs at 0.083 and 0.127 Hz. Chorus + Reverb create an aether zone: above the water column, in the light-saturated surface layer.",
