      "air=1.0 = maximum aether placement",
      "distance=0.8 = far-field spatial positioning"
    ],
    "revelation": "The aether reef exists above the water — in the photon-saturated zone where sound becomes light.",
    "god": "Vangelis",
    "flock_note": "Ruby: 'Turn up your monitors. This preset rewards silence around it.'",
    "diagnosis": "Sound at the threshold of perception — a reef made of atmosphere rather than calcium."
  },
